data.description: BEAUTIFUL LOG CABIN WITH GUEST HOUSE AND PRIVATE POND NESTLED ON OVER 5 ACRES IN CHAPIN! This 3 bed/ 2.5 bath home is full of amazing features! Natural light spills throughout the flowing layout as you move with ease from one room to the next! The huge living room offers ample space to relax and easy access to the kitchen! The spacious and bright eat-in kitchen boasts large island, gorgeous floor-to-ceiling windows and tons of counter and cabinet space making cooking a breeze! The owner's suite features a full, private bath! Each additional bedroom offers ample closet space and access to lovely shared full bath. Immerse yourself in nature surrounded by over 5+ acres with a private pond!
